# Installation

chatbotchat comes without dependencies when using one of the following bots:
- Cleverbot
- Jabberwacky
- Pandorabots

When using the twss bot libsvm is requred
# TWSS Bot
## dependencies
Twss bot requires the following dependencies:
- libsvm-python (or python-libsvm)

## Preparation
This normally should not be necessary as training data are checked in.
If you add training data run the following:

    cd twss
    python preprocessData.py
    python generateTrainTestData.py
    python train.py
